description: Where does Trump stand on the issues? On both sides of course! This hilarious app is based 100% on actual Trump quotes from Twitter, interviews, speeches and books. Donald has very strong opinions and he's not afraid to go head to head with himself to prove he's right. This app is not endorsed, sponsored or approved by Donald Trump.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Trump versus Trump what did Trump say?
Alexa ask Trump versus Trump what does Trump think?
name: Trump versus Trump
shortDescription: Trump vs Trump. Enjoy a one man debate.
